== 榜单表现 ==
由於單曲的提前釋出，《Applause》直接與另一位女歌手[[Katy_Perry|Katy Perry]]的單曲《[[Roar|Roar]]》撞期，在當時引起了社會話題。令兩人的單曲下載和電臺播放形成競爭氣氛。

Nielsen SoundScan曾预计两支单曲在首周达到400,000的数位下载量，<ref name="roarvsapplause">{{cite web|last1=Trust|first1=Gary|last2=Caulfield|first2=Keith|title=Lady Gaga and Katy Perry Singles Could 'Roar' Toward Digital Chart History|url=http://www.billboard.com/articles/news/5647575/lady-gaga-and-katy-perry-singles-could-roar-toward-digital-chart-history|work=[[Billboard_(magazine){{!}}Billboard|Billboard (magazine){{!}}Billboard]]|publisher=[[Prometheus_Global_Media|Prometheus Global Media]]|accessdate=August 14, 2013|date=August 12, 2013|archive-date=2013-08-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130814215438/http://www.billboard.com/articles/news/5647575/lady-gaga-and-katy-perry-singles-could-roar-toward-digital-chart-history|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="applause1stweek">{{cite web|last=Trust|first=Gary|title=Robin Thicke Leads Hot 100 For 10th Week, Katy Perry's 'Roar' Debuts|url=http://www.billboard.com/articles/news/5650672/robin-thicke-leads-hot-100-for-10th-week-katy-perrys-roar-debuts?utm_source=twitter|work=Billboard|publisher=Prometheus Global Media|accessdate=August 14, 2013|date=August 14, 2013|archive-date=2013-09-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130929060116/http://www.billboard.com/articles/news/5650672/robin-thicke-leads-hot-100-for-10th-week-katy-perrys-roar-debuts?utm_source=twitter|dead-url=no}}</ref> 而《Applause》实际销量仅为约200,000~225,000左右<ref name=trustsoar>{{cite web|url=http://www.billboard.com/articles/news/5657773/katy-perry-lady-gaga-soar-at-radio-ahead-of-hot-100-vaults|title=Katy Perry, Lady Gaga Soar At Radio Ahead Of Hot 100 Vaults|last=Trust|first=Gary|date=2013-08-19|work=[[告示牌_(雜誌)|Billboard]]|publisher=Prometheus Global Media|accessdate=2013-08-19|archive-date=2013-08-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130819204450/http://www.billboard.com/articles/news/5657773/katy-perry-lady-gaga-soar-at-radio-ahead-of-hot-100-vaults|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|last=Caulfield|first=Keith|title=Katy Perry Set to Sell 450k Downloads of 'Roar,' Gaga's 'Applause' Set for 225k Debut|url=http://www.billboard.com/biz/articles/news/chart-alert/5657581/katy-perry-set-to-sell-450k-downloads-of-roar-gagas-applause|work=Billboard|publisher=Prometheus Global Media|accessdate=August 16, 2013|date=August 15, 2013|archive-date=2013-08-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130819010833/http://www.billboard.com/biz/articles/news/chart-alert/5657581/katy-perry-set-to-sell-450k-downloads-of-roar-gagas-applause|dead-url=no}}</ref> 。其首周（8月24日）在Billboard Hot 100未入榜（但在Dance/Electronic Songs榜单上排名16， Pop Songs Chart上排名20，打破了2013年Pop Songs Chart上女歌手的最好排名<ref name="trustsoar" />）。而《Roar》首周销量则为557,000，打破了Katy Perry个人之前《Firework》创造的首周销量纪录，并凭借两天里的电台成绩进入Billboard Hot 100榜单85名的位置。

